Media mogul, Mosunmola Abudu, usually known as Mo Abudu  celebrates her birthday with stunning picture as she turns 55 years-old today. The mother of two and Forbes “Africa’s Most Successful Woman”, took to her Instagram page to share beautiful pictures captured by Ty Bello with written appreciation text in indigenous tribes. Mo was born in London, United Kingdom on 11 September 1964. Mo Abudu has won City People Movie Award for Best Movie Producer of the Year (English), City People Movie Special Recognition Award She attended West Kent College, University of Westminster- Law school, The Ridgeway School and Sixth Form College